<i>To dungeons deep</i>

319
00:27:16,118 --> 00:27:20,789
<i>And caverns old</i>

320
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:25,502
<i>We must away</i>

321
00:27:25,503 --> 00:27:30,465
<i>'Ere break of day</i>

322
00:27:30,466 --> 00:27:34,219
<i>To find our</i>

323
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:39,182
<i>Long-forgotten gold</i>

324
00:27:39,183 --> 00:27:42,936
<i>The pines were roaring</i>

325
00:27:42,937 --> 00:27:47,937
<i>On the height</i>

326
00:27:48,234 --> 00:27:49,234
<i>The winds</i>

327
00:27:49,235 --> 00:27:52,195
<i>Were moaning</i>

328
00:27:52,196 --> 00:27:57,196
